{"tid":631913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「TVB」要求封戴耀廷論壇片","createTime":"2018-04-17T02:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T03:40:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d30628f6c9c1d0fa789ce1e5e84e9c1fdb78c2","tid":631913,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T02:11:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180417/20363855?_ga=2.111354884.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F20363855%3F_ga%3D2.111354884.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=HpNC7wmU2S%2F5YZmBUwkU654%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=5e32304b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F20363855%3F_ga%3D2.111354884.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=5bed093c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180417/20363855?_ga=2.111354884.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n「TVB」要求封戴耀廷論壇片<br />\n<br />\n5.2K<br />\n港聞<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180417/large/18666118.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F18666118.jpg&h=96517dd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴耀廷　資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港大法律系副教授戴耀廷上月底赴台出席「台灣青年反共救國團」論壇，惹來「港獨」批鬥風波。救國團理事長楊月清昨指，組織上月底將自行拍攝的論壇片段上載至網站Youtube後，其中一段戴被指涉「講獨」的足本片段，遭名為「TVB」的版權人投訴侵權，一度遭封鎖兩天。楊事後曾向本港無綫電視查詢，對方口頭否認，未有澄清涉事的「TVB」是否無綫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無綫口頭否認涉事<br />\n<br />\n楊指涉事長約25分鐘片段，內容是戴耀廷被指提及港獨的發言片段，只要觀看整段發言，可清楚知道戴非宣揚或鼓吹港獨，「喺咁嘅風頭火勢，點解有人唔想呢段（短片）繼續出街？根本係有心靠害」。楊指該會上月28日將18段論壇短片上載到Youtube，4月6日她收到Youtube通知，因名為「TVB」的版權管理者，聲稱片段涉其版權而封鎖影片。事後她按程序提出申訴，兩天後才獲「TVB」撤銷片段版權聲明，讓片段解封。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n楊指曾向香港無綫電視查詢，對方口頭回覆稱「唔關我哋事」，但拒跟進，亦拒澄清，「事件好奇怪，如果係被冒認，我就唔明白點解咁大間公司都唔愛護自己聲譽，冇下文唔再跟進」。根據Youtube網站所載，版權人可以提交版權侵害通知，要求將涉侵權影片下架，但對方可提出申訴要求恢復播放。在Youtube中，無綫會用「TVB（official）」名稱發佈片段。本報曾向無綫及Youtube所屬的Google查詢，截稿前未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭啟源"},{"pid":"62a7b2e836f41281742db0a1746f3a1d3a3d35ae","tid":631913,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T03:27:53.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5f787dcea91f59c6a88dcee4c85a3d37517d9e7","tid":631913,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"9成9係tvb用人地條片出左新聞，但因tvb係youtube入面算係大版權人，<br />\n<br />\nyoutube系統一scan到兩段片相同，就以為有人偷tvb片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}